parameters.name: 【純愛系】陽だまりのお休みどころ

parameters:
"Uh, how do I solve this problem again? I'm sure if I do
this... and then this..."

"This is an application of the problem we did earlier. If
you calm down and think it through, you should be able to
solve it."

"I see! So this goes like this... and that means... I did
it! I was able to solve it by myself this time, Makoto!"

"That's amazing, Mamoru! Even I find this problem difficult.
To solve it on your own, you must really be working hard!"

"But I'm surprised. You, who hates studying, are asking me
to teach you. Is there a school you want to get into that
badly?"

"Ahaha... well, actually... I'm thinking of applying to the
same school as you, Makoto..."

"I know it's going to be tough with my grades... but we've
been going to the same school for so long, and I want to
keep it that way..."

"I'm... I'm so happy, Mamoru...! Then... I was going to give
this to you the day before the exam, but I'll give it to you
now!"

"This is a charm from a shrine famous for granting success
in exams! Did you go out of your way to buy this for me?"

"D-don't get the wrong idea! This is just something I picked
up when I went to pray..."

"Thank you... really, thank you, Makoto...! I'll definitely
work hard to get into the same school as you!!"

"...Mamoru♡ Then I will also... support you with all my
might! I'm going to teach you even more strictly than usual
today!"

I took out a well-used reference book from the bookshelf and
flipped to the last page. There, along with a supportive
message written by Makoto, was a charm tucked inside. I took
the charm in my hand and clenched it tightly.

"After all the trouble to get into the same school as
Makoto... why did it turn out like this...?"

"No... it's clear, isn't it... it all turned out this way
because of... all because of me..."

(I can hear mom's voice... I don't want to see her right
now... I'll stay in my room for now...)

(It seems like Dad and Mom are discussing something...
Well... eight out of ten times, it's probably about me...)
